Dialogue: 0,-1:59:59.90,-1:59:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:59.90,-1:59:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,-1:59:59.90,-1:59:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.16,0:23:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恢復為日常的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛濺的浪花及大家的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.74,0:23:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而回來的爸爸所帶來的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.64,0:23:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集「蒼穹之戰神」第18話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.45,0:23:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 - 回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.78,0:23:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那裡嗎？
